==Finnish==
===Noun===
'''romaani'''
# book of fiction, [[novel]]
# alternative pronunciation for [[romani]]

===Usage notes===
*The Finns use this term about a "large" book of fiction, and the term [[novelli]] about a [[short story]].
*While [[romani]] is written with one "a" it is often pronunced with two.

